Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,片名：《暂告安全》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁克林，纽约，一小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带过来！轻点，她只是个孩子！\N布鲁克林，纽约，一小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带过来！轻点，她只是个孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我大可以杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在骗我\NYou're lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有！我不知道你在说什么\NI'm not.\NI don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你想要什么，我发誓\NI don't know what you want from me.\NI swear I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我有三个孩子\NI have three children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,作为父亲，首先要学会的\NThe first thing you have to learn\Nas a father is to know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是知道你的孩子何时在欺骗你\Nwhen your children are lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在欺骗我，如果你不说真话\NYou're lying to me,\Nand if you don't stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要用你们那些有名的手段\NI'm going to use one of those tortures\Nyour people are so famous for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来折磨你弱小的身体，直到你告诉我一切\Non your little body\Nuntil you tell me what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次，告诉我那些数字\NFor the last time,\Ngive me the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,204,35倍，是另外一种算法，加起来是350
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,南京，中国，一年前\N204,35倍，是另外一种算法，加起来是350
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果用另外一种算法，加起来是365
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个算法是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,（两人都做错了，定义域是X|X≠-2，\N嘴上说的和黑板上的也牛头不对马嘴）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,苏先生，我没有不尊重你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的算法是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把你转去另一个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我的朋友都在这儿，而且我的妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,梅，你太聪明了，你是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你该上一个特殊的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以找新朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别难过，梅，我们永远都是你的朋友，听说北京的小孩人都很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那儿会过得很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本就不喜欢数学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢我现在的朋友，我不想要交新的朋友，我不喜欢数学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你来做数学，我们给你写信，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每个星期都给你往北京写封信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你发誓？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，你想让我们失去一个有名的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不，梅，我们永远都是你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,梅！\NMei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,新泽西联航中心球馆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还敢来这？\NHow dare you come here!\NYou have no right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈妈！别打了！住手！\N- 你没资格待在这里！没资格！\N- Ma, enough! Stop!\N- You've no right to be here. No right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该被关在监狱里！监狱里！\NYou should be in jail!\NYou should be in jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去！你给我滚出去！\NYou get out of here!\NYou get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起\N- 我要杀掉你！我会杀掉你的！\N- I'm sorry.\N- I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你个废物！那孩子不应该出现在擂台上！\NPiece of garbage. The kid\Nshould never been in there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,路克，别这样！你疯了吗？\NLuke, come on. What, are you crazy, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走开！\N- 给我走开！\N- Get off.\N- Get off, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来都不喜欢你，路克\NI never liked you, Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你比擂台上90%的人都厉害\NYou're a betterfighter than 90%\Nof the guys you go in the cage with,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但你却任人蹂躏\Nbut you just let 'em pound on you\Nlike you're a side of beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你几乎输给过擂台上的每一个笨蛋\NYou already lost to every chump\Nin the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是昨晚\NBut last night, of all nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在第二轮输掉的，你个混蛋\Nyou're supposed to go down\Nin the second, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 仅仅一拳！\N- 退后！\N- Once.\N- Back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就打了他一拳！你从哪里找到他的，操场？\NI hit him once. Where'd you find him,\Nthe fucking playground?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Youtube，你个混蛋\NYouTube, you asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在你把他打晕前，那个孩子还是个网络红人\NThe kid's an internet sensation\Nuntil you put him in a coma,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说，我并不关心这个\Nwhich frankly\NI do not give a shit about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你让我输掉了100万美元\NBut you cost me a million dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然这和你让德切斯基输掉的比起来就不算什么了\Nwhich is nothing\Ncompared what you cost Docheski.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很好！这个名字耳熟吧？\NYeah. You recognise the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他在你身上下了大赌注\NHe was betting on you big time\Nto take the dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他会把这一切都怪罪到我头上来的\NAnd he's gonna take it out on me too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他知道这件事情是我这白痴搞出来的\N'cause he knows I'm the schmuck\Nthat set this whole thing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我把你的脑袋送给他\NUnless I deliver your head\Nwith a down payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道俄国人是什么样子的\NYou know how the Russians are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,梅\NMei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,梅\NMei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的侄女，白玉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,认识吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她在我朋友的班里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她说啊，你的脑筋啊很像电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你的老师讲过了，他也这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑很讨厌，太容易留下痕迹，他们还说...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走开呀，走开！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你学的东西你不会忘的，是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我到你的家，把你的妈妈杀掉好不好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他们说的对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,苏先生告诉我你小的时候你爸爸已经走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妈妈现在很病了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,很快你变成一个人，你喜欢孤独吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放心，我们会好好照顾你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,张，你的新爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他呢会带你漂洋过海，不过那边那里的人呢很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,找我们的麻烦，所以我要你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我们算一算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你打对号码了，有什么事就留言吧\N{\i1}You got the right number,\Nso leave the right message.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,听到后立刻给我回电，安妮，立刻\NCall me when you get this, Annie.\NI mean right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你出去了，别回家\NIf you're out, don't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在吓唬你，记得赶紧回电话\NIf I'm scaring you, that's good.\NCall me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮？\NAnnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样？\NThat's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你是个硬汉啊\NI heard you were\Nsome kind of a tough guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不挣扎下？\NNo fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就直接跪在地上像只求死的狗一样？\NYou're just going to sit on the floor\Nlike a dog who wants to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思搞得那么乱\NSorry it had to be so messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙还在学习中\NThe boy is still learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然不是医生，但我想她有孩子了\NAnd I'm not a doctor,\Nbut I think she was eating for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就像查尔斯·曼森家一样\NWe're like Charlie Manson family, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲本想派其他人来的，但我想锻炼下\NMy father was going to send\Nsomeone else, but I'm making my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你就靠杀害那些没有还手能力的人来锻炼\NYou make your bones by killing someone\Nwho can hurt you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那会是谁呢？你？\NAnd who would that be? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，当然是你\NWell, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚杀了你老婆\NYou just killed your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我没杀她，是你杀的！\NI didn't kill her. You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，你想伤害我？很好\NLook, you want to hurt me? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒想看看你能做些什么\NI want to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我吧\NGet it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了你？你让我父亲输钱，让我的家族难堪\NOver? You cost my father money,\Nmade my family look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们想把你作为一个特例对待\NNow we're going to make\Nan extra special example out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们查过你的档案，没有什么有趣的东西\NSo, we looked into your records.\NNot much to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为城市的卫生系统工作\NWork for city,\Ngarbage collection, sanitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,收益不错，但是缺乏魅力，不是么？\NGood benefits but no glamour, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,父母双亡，没有兄弟姐妹\NFather and mother dead,\Nno brothers or sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是糟糕\Nwhich is too bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想把他们都干掉的\Nbecause I would like\Nto take them from you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你爱你的老婆，我们知道这点\NBut you love your wife.\NWe know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，这样子说定了：\NSo here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了，不过我们会盯着你的\NYou're free to go,\Nbut we will have eyes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一直，但是我们会在你最不希望出现的时候出现\NNot always, but when\Nyou least expect it, we'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,任何一个你想结交的人，甚至是交谈过的\NAnyone you try to make friends with\Nor even talk to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是有过任何交集的人\Nother than ordering a hot dog\Nor something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,都会像你老婆一样因你而死\Nwill die, like your wife,\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当然你可以随时结束这一切！跳桥\NOf course, you can always end it,\Njump off a bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,卧轨\Nthrow yourself in front of a train,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,将你的不朽的灵魂送去地狱，如果你相信这些狗屁\Ndamn your eternal soul to hell,\Nif you believe in that kind of bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就我个人来说，我不相信\NPersonally, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，如果我是你，我宁愿去自杀\NSo I'd go for it if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不是你\NBut I am not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\NThank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以做你想做的事吧\NSo do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你明天还在这，我们会杀掉房东\NIf you're still here tomorrow,\Nwe're going to kill the landlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她叫什么名字？\N- 特巴洛斯基\N- What was her name?\N- Tobolovsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,特巴洛斯基夫人\NMrs Tobolovsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NNice lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾一下吧，清洁工\NClean up the mess, garbage man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好了！她是你女儿，她也是美国公民\NAll right, she's your daughter\Nand she's an American citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会打听你们的关系，这是你们的事\NI ain't gonna ask what the deal is\Nwith her. That's your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想说的是，找关系是很困难的\NBut I'm gonna tell you,\Npulling strings is hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,困难的工作一般不会免费\Nand hard work don't come free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,开个价吧，沃夫队长\NYour price, Captain Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,中国城辖区多交20%\NChinatown precinct take goes up 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗克斯，布鲁克林每个月各涨10%\NBronx 121st, Brooklyn divisions,\Neach go up by 10%, monthly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个价格对于一个小女孩的护照和文书工作来说太过分了\NThat's a steep price for a passport\Nand some papers for a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的日子都不好过啊\NThings are tough all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,中国城加10%\NChinatown gets upped 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗克斯和布鲁克林不变\NBronx and Brooklyn will settle\Nfor the current rate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们在感受到压力的时候\Nand the fact\Nthat we won't start shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不会随意射杀街上的警察和警察家属\Ncops and their families in the streets\Nlike dogs at the first sign of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的日子都不好过啊\NThings are tough all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，朋友，我见过你，我看过你在新泽西的拳击\NHey, man, I know you.\NI saw yourfight in Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是太棒了，你轻松干掉了那家伙\NIt was really good.\NYou knocked that guy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是的\N- 我有好东西，兄弟\N- No.\N- That was some good shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的格斗\NGreat fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,卫路的店，这个礼拜是两万六千，上个礼拜是二十六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,侯进每个礼拜是正好一万五千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他在博易街的店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,中国城，纽约，一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,五月份在丢钱，但是七月八月份他就赚回来了\N中国城，纽约，一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,五月份在丢钱，但是七月八月份他就赚回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,邵成，上个礼拜是42，这个礼拜是42.5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,每个月盈利增长7%
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,莫特区整个盈利总共上升了72535
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从梁先生那里拿了5%
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都每个礼拜盈利6千到8千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,赌场呢？\NThe casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,上个礼拜是八十万，这个礼拜也是八十万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,80万整？\NExactly 800,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大约80万\NIt's almost 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是问你是不是大概80万\NI'm not asking you if it's almost 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要准确数字\NI want the exact number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,78万5370美元\N$785,370.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再上一周呢？\N- 在亏钱\N- And the week before?\N- It's losing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要打了，拜托，不要打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚，你们会有一个新的场上工头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果钱又少了，那就不知道谁会走！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今天晚上他请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不是我请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定你啊，这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他赢了这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么？\N- 为什么？\N- What?\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他损害了生意，生意是件很严肃的事情\NBecause he was hurting business,\Nand business is a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂生意\NI understand business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然要杀他，为什么还要打他？\NBut why beat him\Nif you were going to kill him anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你还是不懂这个生意，不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吃你的饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,靠，靠！\NFuck you. Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能进来\N- 我只想要些吃的！\N- You can't come in the shelter.\N- Just trying to get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧睡觉！5分钟后熄灯\NWrap it up. Lights out in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧睡觉\NWrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好鞋子\NNice kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最好早上它们还在，不然你就得用耳朵穿上它们了\NThey'd better be here in the morning\Nor you'll be wearing them on your ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我会把你的脚给扭下来\N'cause I'll chew yourfeet off\Nat the goddamn ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的想要双新点的鞋子，我会为你做任何事情\NI could really use some new shoes, man.\NI'll do whatever you want, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,任何能帮你熬过晚上的事情\NWhatever gets you through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能...\N- 闭嘴，闭嘴！\N- I just... I can't take another...\N- Shut up. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，拿走吧，我还有旧鞋子\NShut up and take them.\NI've still got my old ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好好照顾你的脚\NGo and get those feet looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都烂掉了\NGangrene's setting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的，谢谢你，朋友\NI will. Thank you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你，兄弟，上帝保佑你\NJesus loves you, brother.\NJesus loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,熄灯了，明早七点会叫醒你们的\N{\i1}Lights out. Wake-up call's 7am.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,熄灯\N{\i1}Lights out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,熄灯\N{\i1}Lights out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\NShh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,梅，我有个坏消息\NMei, I have sad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到他们在谈论…你妈妈走了\NI heard them talking and...\Nyour mother is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她两周前在医院去世了\NShe died two weeks ago in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会告诉你的\NThey werert going to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我告诉你，这样子你可以为她的灵魂祈祷\Nbut I'm telling you\Nso that you can pray
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让她找到去天堂的路\Nfor her soul to find its way to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉他们，如果他们发现我告诉你…\NPlease don't say anything.\NIf they find out I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保密的，谢谢\NI won't say anything. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人起床！9点前离开这里\N{\i1}Everybody up.\NShelter needs to be cleared by 9am.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在3：30前办好今晚的床铺预定\N{\i1}Bed reservations for tonight\Nneed to be made by 3:30.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,带走所有个人物品\N{\i1}Please remove\Nall your personal belongings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人起床！走了！\NEverybody up. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,带好个人物品，你们知道规矩的\NTake your belongings with you.\NYou know the drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，告诉我们发生了什么\NSo you wanna tell us what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有人喜欢那鞋子\NSomeone liked his shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,搞笑的家伙！你认为这是个玩笑？\NFunny guy. You think this is a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道的，你们这帮保安有多糟糕\NYou know, you guys\Nare a hell of a crack security squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的很对，你本来可以说些什么的\NYou were right here.\NYou could have said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你喝醉酒忙着睡觉，是不是？\NBut you were too busy\Nsleeping off this contraband, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果再来这个避难所\NCome into this shelter again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把你踹到大街上去\Nand I'm gonna run your raggedy ass\Nback out into the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:18:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,梅，到你房间去记住这些数字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这些数字很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你妈，你要认真一点，知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的记住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以给你重复一遍，但是又长又无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你看，还没到一年呢，她已经自信的很了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果，她说她可以背出密码，她就能背出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要交给你一个很重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！走路不看路的？\NHey! Watch where you're going, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要给你点颜色瞧瞧？\NYou could get your ass\Nkicked for that, OK? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,4块5毛5\N4.55.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你没钱就得出去\NIf you got no money,\Nyou gotta get out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我有钱\NI got money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有钱，看看他那样子\NHe doesn't have any money.\NLook at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，我告诉过你，如果你没钱，你得离开，懂吗？\NMister, I told you, if you don't\Nhave money, you have to leave, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让开，还有人在等呢\NYou gotta get out of line.\NPeople are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走开，兄弟，让开\N{\i1}Come on, buddy. You gotta go.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这家伙惹麻烦了吗？\N- 他疯了，长官\N- This guy giving you trouble?\N- He's crazy, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把他带出去，好吗？\N- 好的，过来，我们走\N- Get him out of here, OK?\N- All right, come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你！过来，我们走！出去！到街上去！\NHey, you, come on. Let's go.\NOut. On the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们，如果你想当小丑，去马戏团\NLet's go, funny boy. You wanna be\Na clown, go join the circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别在我辖区闹事，听懂了吗？\N我不想在这附近再见到你，嘿！\NNot in my precinct, you hear me?\NI don't wanna see you around here. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\NJesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我抓到了谁\NLook what the cat dragged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看着他\N- 看着他？\N- Look at him.\N- Look at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不去闻闻？\NHow about the smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话叫大家过来\NThink I'll call the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,梅，这是你的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,张会带你见一个人，那个人会给你一个新的数字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,记住那个数字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢张会带你去一个地方，你会得到最后的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想我们吗，伙计？\NYou miss us, partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\NWelcome back to the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,梅…\NMei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你学的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果干的好，你会跟着韩叔前途无量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我不能让他们抓到你\NI'm sorry. I can't let them have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,梅！回来这里！\NMei! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 日子过的怎么样，路克？\N- 悲剧，不过正在变好\N- How's your day been, Luke?\N- Started lousy. But it's looking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,路克·莱特，以前纽约最佳警察\NLuke Wright, the Big Apple's hardest cop\Nonce upon a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都敢试，但你知道你真正的才能吗？\NYou always could take a shot.\NBut you know what your real talent is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个牵线人！我是说，谁会想到\NYou're a uniter. I mean, who'd\Nhave thought that us and the Russkies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会和俄国佬拴在一起？\Nwould ever be on the same page\Nabout anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我！很高兴见到你，混蛋！\NNot me. Nice to see you, rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你出卖我们，我就一直想这么做了\NBeen wanting to do this ever since the\Nday you opened your big fucking mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们听说德切斯基如何对付你时，我笑惨了\NWhen we heard what Docheski did to you,\NI mean, I had to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对于安妮我们很抱歉\NI mean, we felt bad for Annie ar all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道她和谁在一起\NThem's the breaks.\NShe knew who she was with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,街上有流言说你回来的时候\NWord come up from the street\Nyou were back,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至不敢相信\Nwe couldn't believe our fucking ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么回来？为什么不远走高飞？\NWhy would you come back? Why wouldn't\Nyou disappear somewhere far way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说月球\NLike the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想家了\NI missed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾是我们一员，路克，我们曾是一个团队，一个家庭\NYou were one of us, Luke.\NWe were a team. We were family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后你扔下了我们\N- 我们曾经有多风光，混蛋\N- Then you threw us under the bus.\N- We were kings, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，我们只是一群可怜虫\NNow we're bunch of goddamn serfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，嘿，冷静，伯努瓦\NHey, hey, easy, Benoit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当你回来的时候，我们以为你想寻死\NWhen you came back,\Nwe figured you wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:22:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还开了个盘口赌你怎么死，你知道的\NWe got a pool going on when\Nyou're gonna end it and how, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,公交，火车…\Nbus, train...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我赌“找警察自杀”\NI got my money on suicide by cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，拿好了\NCome on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来一枪，来吧\NTake a shot. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮在等着你\NAnnie's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是，你真的认为她想再见到你吗\NQuestion is, do you really think\Nshe wants to see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我真正的才能是让别人输钱\NActually, my real talent\Nis costing other people money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就应该知道的，拉斯基\NYou ought to know that, Lesky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你会输钱的，除非你朝我背后开枪\NYou're gonna lose that bet.\NUnless you wanna shoot me in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不过对你来说也不是第一次了\NWouldrt be your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不了结这一切？\NWhy don't you just end it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你在等什么？\NWhat are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,身边的人死去更多？\NMore people around you to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在等什么？\NWhat are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次，告诉我那些数字\NFor the last time,\Ngive me the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个勇敢的女孩，而且很聪明\NYou're a very brave girl, and clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道我们如何知道你的本事吗？\NBut do you know how we knew exactly\Nwhat you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要在什么时间去什么地方\Nwhere you're going to be and when?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人告诉你了\N- 对\N- Someone told you.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,猜猜是谁？\NCan you guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.32,0:24:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友，告诉你关于你可怜母亲事情的人\NYourfriend, the one who told you\Nabout your poor mother
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,将你从家里带走的流氓可不会告诉你那些\Nwhen the scum\Nwho took you from home would not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.16,0:24:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她在帮我们做事\NShe's working for us with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.91,0:24:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,玲\NLing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.97,0:24:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,梅，我跟他们讲他们想知道的事情\N他们给了我一把一把的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.35,0:24:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，你要是这么做他们也会帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.60,0:25:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是个笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.89,0:25:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,讲英语\NIn English.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.51,0:25:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道生意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.59,0:25:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了他们想要的东西，现在他们要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.81,0:25:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了，讲英语！\NI said speak in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.19,0:25:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？\NWell?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.15,0:25:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她不肯告诉我任何事\NShe won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲很有耐心\NMy father is a patient man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.07,0:25:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\NI am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.70,0:25:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他他想知道的一切\NTell him what he wants to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就…\NOr I'II...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.79,0:25:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约警察！开门！\NNYPD! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.12,0:25:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞什么？\N- 我们是警察\N- What the hell?\N- This is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.08,0:25:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接到报警说扰民\NWe got reports of a disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.76,0:25:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以选择配合或者硬来\NLook, you can make this easy\Nor you can make it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.22,0:25:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,开门，不然我们就要砸门了\NOpen the door or we come in by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.97,0:25:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放屁\NBullshit, blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢进来就别想活着出去，我以母亲之名发誓\NYou come in here, you go out feet first,\NI swear on my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.40,0:25:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在里面，队长\NYeah, they're in there, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.11,0:25:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一点都不配合，你最好在事情失控前过来\NThey're not cooperating. You better\Nget down here before things go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.82,0:26:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，这事闹大了\NNegative, negative. This is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.15,0:26:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回警局指挥，我们再联系\NI'm going back to the station to monitor\Nthe city. I'll get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.28,0:26:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，我们找到她了，你知道我想要什么\NAll right, we got 'em pinned down.\NYou know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.62,0:26:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有言在先，抓到女孩，可以就活捉，不行就干掉\NWe have a deal. Get the girl,\Nalive if you can, dead if you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.63,0:26:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去的话，布鲁克林上升10%，这是新的约定\N{\i1}We go in, Brooklyrs take\Ngoes up by 10%. That's the new deal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.63,0:26:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，我有个电话要接\N{\i1}Hold on, I got an incoming call.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.05,0:26:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿，埃米尔，怎么了？\N- 把你的人弄走，混蛋\N- Emile, what's up?\N- Take your men off, Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.43,0:26:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不管中国人给你什么，我都加5%\NWhatever the Chinese offered to you,\NI'll up it by 5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.35,0:26:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带回来\NGet her back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.70,0:26:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，关\N{\i1}All right, Quan,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.08,0:26:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,俄罗斯人提供我布鲁克林7%\N{\i1}I got the Russians\Noffering to up Brooklyrs take by 7%,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗克斯也一样，所以我不知道该怎么和你说\NBronx the same.\NSo I don't know what to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.33,0:26:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手下，他们宁愿去打仗\NMy guys are willing\Nto go to war over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.58,0:26:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卡在我们和俄国人之间\NYou're gonna be stuck between us\Nand the Russians like Hitler,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.17,0:27:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就像希特勒双线作战，所以你要想清楚\Nfighting on two fronts,\Nso you better think hard about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.38,0:27:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,10%，两个区域，最终提案\N10%, both precincts, final offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.02,0:27:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，麦克，这两帮家伙都愿意\NHey, Mac. Both these bastards\Nare willing to pay a stiff price
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.23,0:27:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为这小姑娘出大价钱\Nfor this little Chink girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.03,0:27:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不管她有什么，我想要\N- 那我们的计划是？\N{\i1}- Whatever she's got, I want it.\N- So what's our play?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.20,0:27:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我让俄国人放下武器，你们进去\N{\i1}I get the Russians\Nto drop their guard, you go in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.82,0:27:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她中枪了\N{\i1}She catches a bullet,\NI want you to take out every last one{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.49,0:27:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我把布尔什维克的都干掉\N{\i1}of those Bolshevik scumbags.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.24,0:27:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，埃米尔，你的提议不错\NAll right, Emile, your offer's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.75,0:27:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让我的人撤走的，只因为我更喜欢你！\N{\i1}I'm gonna call my guys off,\Nbut only 'cause I like you better.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.17,0:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,狗屁！你是个贪婪的混蛋，沃夫\NBullshit. You're a greedy bastard, Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.84,0:27:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的嗅觉很灵敏，你想把一切占为己有\NYou got the scent of something big\Nand now you want it all for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.38,0:27:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我想在你派手下进来前告诉你些事情\NBut I have to tell you something before\Nyou send your men in guns blazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.35,0:27:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她不见了\N- 你指什么，她不见了？\N{\i1}- She's gone.\N- What do you mean, she's gone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.18,0:27:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她逃走了，你的人堵在外面我没法追她\N{\i1}I mean she escaped, and with\Nall your men out there, I can't follow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.73,0:28:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我提议在找到她之前我们停战\N{\i1}I offeryou a truce until we find her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.15,0:28:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓，如果中国人先找到她\N{\i1}Trust me, the Chinese find her first,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.82,0:28:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你会为此后悔一辈子的\N{\i1}that will be a thing you regret\Nas long as you live.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.91,0:28:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,德切斯基，她到底知道些什么？\NDocheski, what does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.41,0:28:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说定了吗，沃夫队长？\N{\i1}Do we have a truce, Captain Wolf?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.62,0:28:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩是中国人，11岁\NThe girl is Chinese, 11 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.38,0:28:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,会说普通话和英语\NShe speaks Mandarin and English.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.09,0:28:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,照片已经下发\NA photo is being disseminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.84,0:28:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,找到她后直接带她去中心大街\NYou are to find her\Nand bring her straight to Centre Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.06,0:28:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她在往地铁去\NShe's heading for subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.42,0:28:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,警察跟我们干上了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.57,0:28:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.48,0:28:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.99,0:28:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个不动脑筋的笨蛋,如果你让警察
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.59,0:28:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,或俄国人先找到那个女孩,我就砍了你人头
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.00,0:29:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.37,0:29:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，安妮\NSorry, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.75,0:31:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,俄国人的手机信号在J大街消失了\NLost my lock\Non the Russian cell on Jay Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.21,0:31:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来他们是进了地铁站\NSounds like they went into\Nthe subway station. Manattan bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.13,0:32:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.87,0:33:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你？那个清洁工？\NYou? The garbage collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.16,0:33:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的情报太糟糕了\NYou've got bad information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.58,0:33:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不收垃圾\N我只丢垃圾\NI never collected garbage.\NI disposed of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:34:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别被吓得失眠了，他应得的\NDon't lose sleep. He had it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.96,0:34:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.05,0:34:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出去！出去！\N- 快\N- Get out! Get out!\N- Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.47,0:34:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\NIt's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.15,0:35:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,最后目击到女孩进了J大街地铁站，红色警报\N{\i1}Girl was last seen entering\NJay Street Station. Red alert.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.70,0:35:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦找到，立刻带她到中央大街的沃夫队长这\N{\i1}Once found, she needs to be brought\Nto Captain Wolf at Centre Street.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.95,0:35:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,重复，红色警报\N{\i1}Repeat, red alert.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.55,0:35:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，孩子，我们是警察\NWhoa. Easy. Easy there, hon.\NWe're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.22,0:35:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了没事了\NEverything's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.22,0:35:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么？孩子\NHey, what's your name, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.10,0:35:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她\NThis is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.27,0:35:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，对我来说他们看起来都一样\NI don't know. They all look alike to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.27,0:35:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有那照片吗？\N- 有，让我看看…\N- You got that picture up?\N- Yeah, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的纽约\NFucking New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没见到某些人的话\NDon't see somebody for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.99,0:35:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你一天会遇到他们两次\NThen you bump into them twice\Nin the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.75,0:35:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你的，孩子\NHey, hey, hey. I'm not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.71,0:36:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么，孩子？\NWhat the hell did you do, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.65,0:36:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这些追你的都是坏人\NYou know, those men chasing you are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.28,0:36:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我他们为什么追你吗\NYou wanna tell me why they're after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.86,0:36:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我在说什么吗？\NYou understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.12,0:36:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你会说英语吗？\NSpeak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.80,0:36:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什姆亚金和其他人消失了是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.44,0:36:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把她带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.77,0:36:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是警察，他还差点干掉几个警察
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.51,0:36:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是中国人，我不知道他到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.18,0:36:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他，活捉女孩，不行就全干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.33,0:37:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走另一边！都是车！\NThe other way! Cars go the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.72,0:37:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\NAre you a crazy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.33,0:38:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,坐稳了\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.96,0:38:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去,很多无辜的人会受伤\NIf this goes on, a lot of\Ninnocent people are gonna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.17,0:38:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望那样子吗?\NYou want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.14,0:38:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很好！那就按我说的做\NGood. Then do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.18,0:38:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\NYou OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.43,0:38:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.06,0:39:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是5岁小孩\NI'm not five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.19,0:39:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就跟上\NThen keep up
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.46,0:39:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们找到后又跟丢了？\N- 不，队长，我们没有跟丢她\N- You had her and you lost her.\N- No, Captain, we didn't lose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.30,0:39:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她被抢走了\NShe was taken by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.76,0:39:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 俄国人？\N- 不是俄国人\N{\i1}- The Russians?\N- No, not the Russians.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.63,0:39:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.43,0:39:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是路克·莱特\N- 什么？\N- It was Luke Wright.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.60,0:39:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沃夫队长\N- 等会，大卫\N- Captain Wolf?\N- Not now, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.31,0:39:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,市长想找你，队长\NThe mayor wants you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.52,0:39:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把他接到2线\N- 不是电话\N- Put him through on two.\N- He's not on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.69,0:39:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让你去大厦…昨天\NHe wants you at the mansion, yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.48,0:39:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,给您\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.16,0:39:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，伊万诺夫先生\N- 谢谢\N- Thank you, Mr Ivanov.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.00,0:40:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万诺夫先生？给您，伊万诺夫先生，1012号房间\NMr Ivanov?\NHere you are, Mr Ivanov. Room 1012.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.09,0:40:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 10楼\N- 谢谢\N- Tenth Floor.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.28,0:40:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢高档酒店？\NYou like a nice hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.95,0:40:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没住过高档酒店\NI've never stayed in a nice hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.91,0:40:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没人会到这种地方找我们\NNo one's gonna look for us in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.12,0:40:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定在这里，不过我看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.63,0:40:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干扰太多
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.13,0:40:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.44,0:40:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.09,0:41:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,多想现在洗个澡啊\NWould I love a shower right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.01,0:41:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以洗的\NYou could use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.48,0:41:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我大可以让俄国人把你带下列车\NI could have just let those Russians\Ngrab you on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.94,0:41:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要救我？\NWhy did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.57,0:41:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我没救你…是你救了我\NI didn't save you. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.74,0:41:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是作为回报\NI'm paying you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.87,0:41:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫路克\NMy name's Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.79,0:41:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,梅\NMei.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.38,0:41:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你有父母吗，梅？\NYou have parents, Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.01,0:41:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有父亲\N- 他叫什么?\N- I have a father.\N- What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.80,0:41:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,张关\NChang Quan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.81,0:41:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,张关？\NChang Quan?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.39,0:41:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们是在说同一个人的话\NIf we're talking about the same guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.27,0:41:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知他根本没孩子\Nhe didn't have any kids\Nlast time I checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.94,0:41:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这没道理，他不可能有像你那么大的孩子\NAny made since\Nwouldn't be a day over three years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.03,0:41:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是领养的\NI'm adopted.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.40,0:42:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他从老家带你来这的？\NHe bring you overfrom back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.12,0:42:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,张不像是个做父亲的人\NChang isn't the fatherly type.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.37,0:42:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么来这，梅？\NWhy are you here, Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.67,0:42:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,做会计\NTo count.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.09,0:42:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是被张的老板，那个老家伙送来的？他叫什么？\NYou were sent over by the old guy,\NChang's boss. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.68,0:42:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没有电脑，没有电子资料\NOld school.\NNo computers, no electronic trails.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.31,0:42:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你脑子里的东西，是吗？\NJust what you have\Nin your head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.61,0:42:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道韩礁吗？\N- 我知道他\N- You know Jiao Han?\N- I know of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.24,0:42:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉了我一个数字，非常长的一个数字\NHe told me a number,\Na very long number.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.54,0:42:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来要去个地方拿下个数字和指示\NI was going someplace where I would get\Nanother number and more instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.21,0:42:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是俄国人现身杀了所有人\Nbut the Russian came and shot everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.67,0:42:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,之后警察又出现了，我就逃走了\NThen the police came and I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.25,0:42:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道一切了，高兴了吗？\NNow you know everything.\NHappiness for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.59,0:43:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想回去找韩礁吗？\NYou wanna go back to Han Jiao?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.85,0:43:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我造成了太多麻烦\N生意搞砸了\NI make too much trouble. Bad business.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.06,0:43:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,事成之后，他会杀掉我，真是如意算盘\NAfter I do what he asks, he kills me.\NGood business.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.10,0:43:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，这组数字是什么？\NSo what about this number?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.44,0:43:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一个又长又无聊的数字，我可以告诉你\NIt's a long, boring number.\NI can tell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.44,0:43:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说毫无意义\NIt wouldn't mean anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.99,0:43:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是一个数字而非一堆独立数字呢？\NHow do you know it's one number\Nand not a bunch of separate numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.70,0:43:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个疯子，但是倒不蠢\NYou're a crazy man but not so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.45,0:43:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这些数字对你来说有何特别吗？\NIs there anything interesting to you\Nabout these numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.58,0:43:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 或许有点\N- 为什么？\N- Maybe a few of them.\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.84,0:43:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们都是3或者7开头\NBecause they have a three or a seven\Nbefore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.96,0:43:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所有数字都是随机的\NAll the numbers are random,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.84,0:43:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但当中5个是7开头的，8个是3开头的\Nbut five of them has a seven before\Nand eight of them has a three before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.26,0:43:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对于随机数来说这频率太高\NThat's too many times to be random.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.93,0:43:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个密码\NIt's a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.48,0:43:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有呢？\N- 没了\N- What else?\N- Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.60,0:43:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，这些3和7是比较有用的\NSo the three and the seven\Nare interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.56,0:44:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们随机出现了太多次？\Nbecause they happen too many times\Nto be random.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.82,0:44:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它们不是数字，是单词\NBecause they're not numbers.\NThey're words.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.11,0:44:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,从左到右或者从右到左\NRight left or left right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.66,0:44:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老手法了，保险箱的密码\NOld school. Combination to a safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.21,0:44:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个酒店里？\NIn the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.51,0:44:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哪？\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我能查到的就是这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.33,0:44:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.65,0:44:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在在找一个男的，他和一个女孩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.90,0:44:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他有武器，非常危险，警察局的人说他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.05,0:44:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大概5尺11寸，褐色头发，30岁左右\NAbout five eleven, brown hair, 30s.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.65,0:44:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大概几小时前来的\NProbably came in here\Nless than a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.99,0:44:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，我们不允许透露顾客信息\NSir, we're not allowed\Nto discuss our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.07,0:44:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，他确实是客人了？他入住了吗？\NSo he's a guest? Did he check in?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.54,0:44:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，先生，我们不能…\NI'm sorry, sir.\NWe're not at liberty to...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.41,0:44:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他和一个中国女孩在一起，11岁\NHe would have been with a Chinese girl,\N11 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.12,0:44:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她的父亲，我很担心她\NI'm herfather\Nand I'm very worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.13,0:45:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉，我可以帮你报警\NI'm so sorry.\NI can call the police for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.42,0:45:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢报警我杀了你\NDo that and I blow your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.38,0:45:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在…\N- 别动\N- Now...\N- Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.55,0:45:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪个房间？\N...what room is he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.68,0:45:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个房间？\N{\i1}What room is he in?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.85,0:45:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…他是在10楼\NI think maybe\NI put him on the 10th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.19,0:45:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个房间？\NRoom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.94,0:45:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓，他没有带着一个小女孩\NI swear he didn't have\Na little girl with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.36,0:45:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 房间\N- 我需要查一下\N- Room.\N- I just need to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.15,0:45:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快查，或者我给你一枪\NThen check quick\Nor I put a bullet in your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.36,0:45:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快\N- 把手举起来\N- Quick.\N- Put your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.58,0:45:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不会想这么做的\N- 把手举高让我看见\N- You don't want any part of this.\N- Hands up so I can see 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.76,0:45:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没人可以离开这酒店\NNo one leaves the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.89,0:45:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.64,0:45:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,1012，他在1012房\N1012. He's in room 1012.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.19,0:46:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你说没人会到这里找我们\NI thought you said\Nno one would look for us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.98,0:46:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它关掉了，没人能打进来\NI turned it off\Nso no one could call when I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.07,0:46:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它不需要被开着\NIt doesn't need to be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.99,0:46:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回去！\N- 等等！\N- Get back!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.07,0:46:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我趴在地上！\NGet down on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.91,0:46:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人回去！\NEverybody back!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.41,0:46:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,写下那些数字\NWrite down the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.62,0:46:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那些3和7开头的，快！\Njust the ones with the three\Nand the seven in front of 'em, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.67,0:46:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你！过来这里！趴下！趴下！\NYou, get over there! Get down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.01,0:46:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想办法带你去安全的地方\NI'll try to get you someplace safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.68,0:46:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们分开了，别说你跟我说过什么！\NWe get separated,\Ndon't tell them you told me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.10,0:46:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 梅，如果他们试图吓唬你…\N- 试图？我已经被吓到了！\N- Mei, if they try to scare you...\N- Try? I'm so scared already.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.81,0:46:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我也是，记住，撒谎！\NYeah, me to. Remember, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.52,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快到了\NWe're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.94,0:46:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们看到他们下楼，小心别杀了那个女孩\NIf you see them downstairs,\Ntry not to kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.40,0:46:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,进去\NBack inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.54,0:47:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上他们！我下楼去断他们退路！\NFollow them!\NI'm going back down to cut them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.49,0:47:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,警察来了，顶住他们直到我下令撤退！\NThe cops are here.\NHold them off until I give the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.12,0:47:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他们进来\NDo not let them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.32,0:48:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人给我趴下，你们走不了了\NEverybody stay down!\NYou ain't going nowhere! Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.20,0:48:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！你去哪？回去！站住！蹲下！都回去！\NHey, where you going?\NGet down! No! Get back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.28,0:48:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回去！\N- 快！快！\N- Get back!\N- Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.17,0:49:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,起来！所有人起来！\NGet up! Everybody up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.26,0:49:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要离开酒店了，起来！\NWe're getting out of the hotel. Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.30,0:49:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来，不然我就开枪了！站起来！\NUp or I start shooting you! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.52,0:49:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,58号转角，我们发现嫌疑犯\NMoving to corner of 58.\NWe got a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.31,0:49:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\NHey, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.73,0:49:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.82,0:49:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,走！往那走！\NMove! Move! Over there! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.58,0:49:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,到街上去，别停！谁不听话下场就是这样！\NInto the street and keep moving!\NAnyone who doesn't dies like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.17,0:49:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,到街上去\NInto the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.75,0:49:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,重复，别开枪！\NRepeat, hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.01,0:49:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那些都是平民！\NThey're civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.69,0:50:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌犯在人群中，嫌犯在人群中\NSuspect is in the crowd.\NSuspect is in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.62,0:50:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！给我站住！\NHey, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.60,0:50:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你干什么！\NHey! What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.90,0:51:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的车！做点什么！他抢了我的车！\NThat's my car!\NDo something, he took my fucking car!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.17,0:51:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,往市中心开，我过一会告诉你地址\NHead downtown.\NI'll give you an address in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.61,0:51:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,靠\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.78,0:51:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿，朋友！可以告诉我地址了吗？\N- 等一下\N- Hey, buddy, you wanna give me address?\N- In a minute. Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.65,0:52:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.73,0:52:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为是谁？我是皮特,你电话里没我号码吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.55,0:52:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,皮特？警察说在地铁里发现你跟...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.39,0:52:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,警方报告有误
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.65,0:52:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人被...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.98,0:52:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.65,0:52:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，信号不好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.07,0:52:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到数字了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.56,0:52:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在她被劫走前，我们从她那拿到数字了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.58,0:52:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟条子玩了几个小时的捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.60,0:52:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伊哥，把数字记到手机里
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.32,0:52:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧，告诉我数字
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.00,0:52:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？数字在一公里外一张纸上，你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.16,0:52:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能带警察来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.41,0:52:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要清场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.18,0:52:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有警察，我们最好避开人群
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.09,0:52:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且需要有利地形
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.68,0:53:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，皮特...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.74,0:53:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在给你个机会做英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.58,0:53:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,曼梦西卡见
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.77,0:53:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.58,0:53:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上到
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.28,0:53:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他回来了？路克·莱特回到我的城市了？\NHe's here? Luke Wright is back\Nin the city, in my city?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.49,0:53:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经回来有一段时间了\N{\i1}He's been back for a while.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.37,0:53:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一段时间？多久？\N- 可能一年，这很难说\N- A while? What's a while?\N- Maybe a year. It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.71,0:53:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,挂掉电话！\NTurn that goddamn thing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.13,0:53:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亚历克斯\N- 朋友们\N- Alex.\N- Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.38,0:53:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是，对不起，市长\NYes, sir. Sorry, Your Honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.59,0:53:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么，沃夫？路克·莱特又是怎么卷进来的？\NWhat's going on, Wolf?\NAnd how's Luke Wright involved in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.26,0:53:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来也想问你这个问题\NI figured I might ask you\Nthe same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.51,0:53:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别和我玩游戏\NDon't try to game me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.60,0:53:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不过就是个马前卒\NYou're nothing but a pawn
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.18,0:53:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下着一盘你无法掌控的大棋\Nplaying on a board so big\Nyou can't even see the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.73,0:53:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已\NThat's all you've ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.77,0:53:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,直到5分钟前我都比你更了解路克·莱特\NI knew about Luke Wright, which is more\Nthan you can say until five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.74,0:53:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你所知的路克·莱特\NWhat you know about Luke Wright
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.28,0:53:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还不到浩瀚资料中的一小片段\Nrates less than a paragraph\Nin a very fat book.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.37,0:53:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,世贸大厦倒下后\NAfter the towers fell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.53,0:53:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人都分散出去追寻恐怖活动\Nand our manpower was spread out\Ntracking terrorist activity,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.66,0:53:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是我组织了特勤队\NI was the one\Nwho formed the special task force
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.62,0:54:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,惩治犯罪以填补缺口\Nto deal with the crime\Nthat was filling the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.58,0:54:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了也是我让你来管理这支队伍\NAnd don't you ever fucking forget that\NI was the one who put you in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.17,0:54:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没忘记…我的工作成就了你的市长\NI didn't forget. My work made you mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.84,0:54:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工作？\NYour work?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.67,0:54:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为路克只是你警察中的一员？\NYou think Luke\Nwas just one of your cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.59,0:54:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当我拉起队伍时，我知道它需要一面刀锋\NWhen I put together your team,\NI knew it needed an edge
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.10,0:54:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,普通警探无法胜任，得像手术刀刀锋一般\Nno ordinary detectives could give me,\Nsomething surgical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.56,0:54:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我拜托那些甚至不存在于官方记录中的朋友\NI called friends in places buried\Nso deep they don't officially exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.31,0:54:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很同情我，一周后他们送来了路克·莱特\NThey were sympathetic.\NA week later they sent Luke Wright.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.74,0:54:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那些过去七年里消失的自作聪明的家伙\NThose wise guys who vanished\Nover the last seven years,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.15,0:54:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为他们死于自相残杀？\Nyou think that was internecine war?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.12,0:54:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哈林区排水沟里找到的可卡因\NThose coke kings\Nyou found in the gutter in Harlem.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.58,0:54:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁克林的弗雷迪·彼得罗维奇，中国城的汤米·劳\NFreddy Petrovich in Brooklyn.\NTommy Lau in Chinatown.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.21,0:54:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,路克·莱特是个幽灵\NLuke Wright is a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.04,0:54:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,非常致命的幽灵\NA very deadly ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.84,0:54:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且工作很效率\NIt worked like a charm too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.67,0:54:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你们这帮混蛋就忙着捞钱了\NThen you dicks had to get greedy\Nand pad your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.43,0:54:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,路克是个杀手，但是个诚实的杀手\NLuke's a killer, but he's an honest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.01,0:54:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当他威胁说要把向情报局告发一切时\NWhen he threatened to take\Nthe whole thing to IA,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.68,0:55:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当时确实费了很大的劲\Nit took some people with a lot of bronze\Nstuck to their pyjamas
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.48,0:55:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才搞定他\Nto talk him off the ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.85,0:55:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我的队伍解散，我们就又变回苦力了\NYeah, my team gets dismantled.\NWe're peons again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.73,0:55:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果路克·莱特有这么深背景\NBut if Luke Wright's so connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.27,0:55:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他会沦落到在泽西打拳击\Nhow does he wind up in Jersey\Ncage fighting on the B circuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.15,0:55:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来像心理医生吗？\NDo I look like a shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.49,0:55:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,动员起所有人来\NGet everybody on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.87,0:55:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦路克·莱特有了目标\NOnce Luke Wright gets on a roll,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.70,0:55:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,整个城市只有一个人能在\N一对一中和他抗衡\Nonly one man in this city\Ncan take him on one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.87,0:55:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了,我知道我不该打扰你们\NI know this is a closed door,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.16,0:55:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是市中心一座酒店发生了大规模枪战\Nbut there was just a major gun battle\Ndowntown at a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.25,0:55:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体都疯了,您需要赶紧做一份声明\NMedia's going nuts.\NYou're gonna need to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.76,0:55:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,韩礁现在也在城里\NHan Jiao is in the city also.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.17,0:55:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他给了那个中国女孩一些东西,我不知道的东西\NHe give this little Chinese girl\Nsomething, I don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.68,0:55:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,路克·莱特在我之前带走了她\NLuke Wright grabbed her before I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.47,0:55:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？\N- 我说路克·莱特\N- What?\N- I said Luke Wright...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.85,0:55:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了，我一开始就听到了\NYeah, yeah, yeah.\NI heard you the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.52,0:55:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭曼哈顿的每一个出口\NClose every exit out of Manattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.19,0:55:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,确保莱特和那个女孩逃不出去\NMake sure that neither Wright or the\Ngirl gets away, you get commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.90,0:55:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放跑了...你就找把铲子自掘坟墓吧\NLet 'em go... you get a shovel\Nto dig your own grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.49,0:55:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩绝不能离开这个城市\NThat girl does not leave this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.20,0:56:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谁杀了那个俄国人?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.60,0:56:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道,他没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.73,0:56:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有问到那个数字？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.65,0:56:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都问那个数字
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.05,0:56:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那你跟他们讲些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.49,0:56:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.08,0:56:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.26,0:56:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.13,0:56:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在撒谎！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.83,0:56:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,韩叔叔我当然不会给你撒谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.56,0:56:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,打个电话告诉他们把阿梅的妈妈干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.48,0:56:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她的女儿是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.53,0:56:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,韩叔叔，我发誓，我假装不会说英文也听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.19,0:56:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们又吼又叫的但是我什么都没说，因为我知道你会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.97,0:57:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我向我妈发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.73,0:57:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找到了女孩，但是信息可能已经被泄漏\NWe recovered the girl, but the\Ninformation might have been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.86,0:57:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们要改下时间表吗？\N- 不可能\N{\i1}- Should we change our time frame?\N- lmpossible.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.53,0:57:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在整件事情已经失控了\NNow that the whole damn thing\Nhas gone supernova,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.86,0:57:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚一定要了结此事\Nit's going to happen\Nand it's gonna happen tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.28,0:57:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,会面地点要改下\NBut the meeting place\Nneeds to be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.99,0:57:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到哪？\N- 我会告诉你的\N- Where to?\N- I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.74,0:57:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里！就这里！\NHere. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.29,0:57:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点，停车\NSlow down. Stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.63,0:57:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行，别把妓女带上我的车子\NNo, no, you don't bring\Nno hookers in my cab, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.22,0:57:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,继续打你的表\NJust keep the meter running.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.22,0:57:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐们\NLadies.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.60,0:57:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去喝一杯如何？\NHow about a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.15,0:57:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好\NGood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.32,0:58:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 晚上好\N- 想在这里吃晚餐吗？\N- Evening.\N- Will you be joining us for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.32,0:58:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们没有预定\N- 没事的\N- We don't have a reservation.\N- That's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.08,0:58:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚虽然很忙，但是我们应该能给你们找到位置\NWe're busy tonight, but we should\Nbe able to find you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.42,0:58:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,楼下已经没有空位了，不过背后还有些\NWe don't have any tables downstairs,\Nbut there are some in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.09,0:58:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,或者如果你们喜欢的话，去楼上也可以\NOr you could sit upstairs if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.39,0:58:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,先生？您怎么看？先生？\NSir? Sir?\NDo you have a preference? Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.89,0:58:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就在吧台喝点酒\NI think we'll just get a drink\Nat the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.27,0:58:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你亲我一下然后转身出去\NI want you to give me a kiss,\Nturn round and walk out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.65,0:58:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我以为\N- 就像你忘记了什么东西一样\N- But I thought...\N- Just act like you forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.49,0:58:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不要再回来了\NOnly don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.29,0:58:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来杯白俄罗斯，还有把叉子\NGive me a white Russian, please,\Nand a fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.96,0:58:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 叉子？\N- 就那样的\N- Fork?\N- One of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.08,0:59:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不知这种时候该说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.12,0:59:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.30,0:59:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在我杀人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.54,0:59:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他开的什么车？停在哪？\NWhat does he drive\Nand where is it parked?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.67,0:59:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,外面小路上的一辆银色的SUV\NA silver SUV in the alley outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.61,1:00:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瓦西里\N- 打错了\N{\i1}- Vassily.\N- Not even close.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.78,1:00:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\NWho is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.95,1:00:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,整晚都在屠戮你手下的人，埃米尔\NThe guy who's been\Nkilling your boys all night, Emile.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.24,1:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的儿子在我手里\NThe guy who has your son tied up\Nin a very dark place.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.33,1:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听好，我想要…\NNow, here's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.49,1:00:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我会关心你想要什么？\N{\i1}You think I give a shit\Nof what you want?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.29,1:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为抓了瓦西里就能敲诈我？\NDo you think you can blackmail me\Nbecause you have Vassily?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.79,1:00:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杀了他，下地狱去吧\N- 我会下地狱的\N{\i1}- Kill him and go to hell.\N- I'm going to hell all right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.67,1:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我不会杀了你儿子\N{\i1}But I'm not gonna kill your boy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.17,1:00:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把他带在身边，就像宠物一样\N{\i1}I'm gonna keep him around, like a pet.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.84,1:00:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我对待宠物可不友善\NA very badly treated pet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.68,1:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会做一些让我以后每次照镜子\NI'm gonna do things to him\Nthat'll make me ashamed
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.76,1:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都觉得屈辱的事情，但是我会这么做的\N{\i1}to look in the mirror afterward,\Nbut I will do them.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.60,1:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦西里会告诉我所有他所知道的\N{\i1}Vassily's gonna tell me everything\Nhe knows about your operation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.23,1:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你准备怎么做？报警？\NAnd then what you gonna do?\NTell the police?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.94,1:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在搞笑吗？\N- 我之前有提到过警察吗？\N- You want me to laugh?\N- Who said anything about the police?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.57,1:00:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把这些信息与你的竞争对手分享\NI'm gonna share the information\Nwith the competition,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.90,1:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没干掉的那些家伙\Nthe ones I haven't already killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.74,1:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我会拿光你所有的东西\N{\i1}Anything they don't take from you,\NI will.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.37,1:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我会带走你漂亮的老婆\N{\i1}First I'm gonna take your trophy wife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.83,1:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是你的孩子们\N{\i1}Then I'm gonna take\Nyour trophy children.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.96,1:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你一无所有\N{\i1}I'm gonna leave you with nothing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.63,1:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当我完事后，你就什么都不是了\NWhen I'm done, you won't even be\Na memory of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.34,1:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不过这些都没必要发生\N- 你想要什么？\N{\i1}- But that doesn't have to happen.\N- What do you want?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.67,1:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想知道保险箱里有什么\N- 什么保险箱？\N- I wanna know what's in the safe.\N- What safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.09,1:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩给我密码的那个保险箱\NThe safe the girl gave me\Nthe combination to. That safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.52,1:01:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,三千万美元\N{\i1}$30 million.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.19,1:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子本来要去拿第二个密码，第二个保险箱里有什么？\NKid was on her way to get a second\Nnumber. What's in the second safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.11,1:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,值三千万美元的东西\N{\i1}Something won'th $30 million.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.90,1:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给谁？\N- 不知道\N{\i1}- To who?\N- No idea.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.61,1:01:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为你只有小聪明，埃米尔\NThat's 'cause\Nyou're only half-smart, Emile.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.24,1:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我们这么说定了…\NSo here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.16,1:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我第一个保险箱在哪，我拿了钱就放你儿子\NYou tell me where the first safe is,\NI take the money and let your boy go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.04,1:01:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,骗我的话你就死定了，说到做到\N{\i1}Lie to me and yourworld ends.\NYou have my word on that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.96,1:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴！我知道一个人是否独行\NIdiot. I know\Nwhen a man is working alone
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.17,1:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而你正好只身一人\Nand you're as alone as one can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.80,1:01:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要一支队伍才能靠近保险箱\NYou need a small army\Nto get near that safe,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.89,1:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我有这种队伍\Nthe kind of army I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.22,1:01:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经有过！我时间不多\NHad. It's been shrinking by the minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.44,1:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次机会，否则我就挂电话修理你儿子了\N{\i1}Last chance before I hang up\Nand go to work on your son.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.86,1:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你要杀我吗，收垃圾的？\NGoing to kill me, garbage man?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.45,1:02:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你那天就可以把我们都干掉的，是吗？\NYou could have taken us out that day,\Ncouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.91,1:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你只是跪在那里\NBut you just sat there,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.20,1:02:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们毁掉你，让你变得一无是处\Nlet us ruin you,\Nlet us make you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.08,1:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是保险箱给了你新的动力，是吗，收垃圾的？\NI guess finding out about that safe gave\Nyou new motivation, eh garbage man?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.42,1:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是你就不会浪费口舌\NI wouldn't spend my time talking\Nif I were you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.59,1:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,会祈祷事情结束时，那小女孩还活着\NSpend it praying that when this is over\Nthat little girl's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.76,1:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,祈祷！\NPray.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.02,1:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,时间地点？\NWhen and where?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.19,1:02:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,桥下的地下道，一小时后\N{\i1}The underpass under the bridge,\None hour.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.07,1:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，那些俄国人出现时我用枪指着你\NI'm sorry I pointed a gun at you\Nwhen the Russians attacked us, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.41,1:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那只是…\N- 生意而已…我知道的\N- It was...\N- Business. I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.54,1:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，很好，你理解\NIt's good. It's good you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.13,1:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会搞定这一切\NWe're going to get this done
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.38,1:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你跟我和韩叔一起就安全了\Nand you'll be safe\Nwith me and Uncle Han.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.42,1:03:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证做一个好父亲\NI promise to be a better father to you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.13,1:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,比那个抛弃你和你母亲的家伙更好\Nthan the one\Nwho left you and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.06,1:03:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界上没人比我更关心你\NThere's no one in the world\Nwho cares more about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.06,1:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的，是吗？\NYou know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.68,1:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,人都到了\NWell, the gang's all here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.14,1:03:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多\NAlmost.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.10,1:04:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伯尼生病了？\N- 他在医院，混蛋！\N- Reddick have to call in sick?\N- He's in the hospital, dickhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.52,1:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你打坏了他的气管\N- 我从来不知道气管还能被打坏\N- You broke his trachea.\N- I didn't know a trachea could break.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.40,1:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 希望他们能修好\N- 是吗！不如让我先修理你？\N- Hope they can fix it.\N- Yeah? How about I fix you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.52,1:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！嘿！嘿！嘿！别这样！\NHey, hey, hey, hey. Not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.23,1:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见，路克，不过我并不想念你\NIt's been a while, Luke.\NCan't say I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.28,1:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那么，有话直说吧\N- 带了我要的东西没？\N- So, let's get down to business.\N- Did you bring what I asked for?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.54,1:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 托斯卡尼的\N- 还有呢？\N- Toscanni's.\N- Where else?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.73,1:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,味道不错！\NMmm. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.58,1:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我整晚都在餐馆里\NBeen in restaurants all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.66,1:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们提供给我的都是子弹\NAll I got served was lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.96,1:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有火吗？\N- 去你的！\N- Anyone got a light?\N- You know what? Screw this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.09,1:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，队长，你让我们过来，我们过来了\NLook, Captain, you asked us\Nto come here, so we came.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.76,1:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会站在这里听这混蛋胡扯\NBut I ain't gonna sit here\Nand listen to this scumbag's big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.55,1:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，科夫克斯！\NShut up, Kolfax.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.14,1:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还没戒烟，哈？\NStill haven't quit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.15,1:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，嘿，这是什么？\NHey. Hey, what the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.95,1:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,装有三千万美元保险箱的密码\NCombination of the safe\Nwith 30 million bucks in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.12,1:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哇，哇！你在干嘛？\N- 你个狗屎\N- Whoa, whoa, whoa.\N- Filthy piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.79,1:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这密码存在我脑子里了\NThe only place it exists now is in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.87,1:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,当你们手痒想扣扳机时，记住这点\NRemember that next time\Nyour little triggerfinger gets itchy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.58,1:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么韩礁会把它藏在\NWhy would Han Jiou stash it
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.00,1:05:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,中国城最繁忙的赌窝里？\Nright in the middle of Chinatowrs\Nbusiest gambling den?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.80,1:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为伯努瓦这样的喜欢\NBecause of sleaze-bucket cops\Nlike you, Benoit,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.13,1:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去赌窝收保护费腐败警察\Nwho collect off of Chinatowrs\Nbusiest gambling den.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.84,1:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想不吸引警察的注意\NWhere else would he surround it\Nwith dozens of armed man
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.43,1:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他还能放在哪里？\Nwithout attracting police attention?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.18,1:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,队长,我们怎么知道这混蛋不是在玩我们？他是个流浪汉！\NCaptain, why do we know this son of\Na bitch on the level, huh? He's a bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.81,1:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪得到的消息？\NWhere'd you get your information?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.73,1:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚会有个交易\NThere's an exchange happening tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.94,1:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,三合会半数交易额都在赌场保险箱里\NThe Triad half of the deal\Nis in a safe in the casino.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.27,1:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我一人搞不定，所以我叫了你们，老朋友们\NNo way I could get to it on my own,\Nso I called on you, my old pals.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.32,1:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,三千万美元分六份依然是很大一笔钱\N30 million split six ways\Nis still a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.62,1:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们风险太大，队长，尤其是你\NWe're risking a lot, Captain.\NYou especially.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.71,1:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都知道你前途光明\NEverybody knows you got a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.46,1:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁保证的？你的市长？\NPromised by who? His Honour?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.59,1:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟你承诺什么了，沃夫？\NWhat carrot\Nis he teasing you with, Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.46,1:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,若他知道你所掌握的，他还会放过你？\NHe's gonna let you out in the street\Nknowing what you know now?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.01,1:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思？\NWhat's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.34,1:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是，他的第二任期快到头了，什么保证都是屁\NHis second term is gonna come to an end\Nand his hold on the city goes poof.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.39,1:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟普通公民一样\NJust like that he's Joe Citizen again.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.97,1:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三千万是一笔不错的退休金\N30 million would be\Na nice retirement package.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.43,1:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他给中国佬什么好处？\NWhat's he giving the Chinks?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.85,1:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我知道，还会跟你们这帮混蛋站在这里？\NIf I knew that, I wouldn't be standing\Nhere with you assholes, would I?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.44,1:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,光明未来，哈？\NA bright future, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.19,1:06:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,头条\NBig headlines.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.07,1:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“英雄警察破获纽约最大的地下赌博巢穴”\N"Hero cops take down New York City's\Nbiggest underground gambling operation."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.70,1:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,每人五百万美元，且没人知道\NFive million bucks apiece\Nthat no one will ever know about,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.87,1:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就当是额外甜头\Njust to give it that extra sweet taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.01,1:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，谁进去过？拜托，谁进去过？\NAll right, who's been in there?\NFor Christ's sake, who's been in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.14,1:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我，队长\N- 你俩做先锋\N- Me, Cap.\N- You two, you're on point.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.65,1:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,里面都是平民，看准了打\NPlace is packed with civilians,\Nso exercise some judgement.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.61,1:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,记住只有我有密码\NRemember, I got the combination.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.90,1:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们想要钱，掩护好我\NYou want that money, watch my back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.50,1:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.76,1:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！待着！\NDon't move! Stay!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.44,1:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让开！走！\NOut of the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.50,1:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你，去死吧！\NHey, you, settle down!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.22,1:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里！走！\NThis way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.06,1:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\NHeads up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.74,1:09:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,走\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.92,1:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,科夫克斯，干掉他\NKolfax, take him out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.55,1:10:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护他\NCover him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.76,1:10:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,打开它，开枪！\NOpen it. Take it!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.35,1:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,靠！\NOh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.53,1:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,靠！我必须离开这里\NOh, shit.\NI gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.62,1:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,操，操，队长\NOh, fuck. Fuck, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.04,1:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，你个混蛋！你杀了同伴，你个混蛋！\NGod, you shit!\NShoot a man in the back, son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.30,1:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了，米尔斯，我们往哪走？\N- 这里\N- All right, Mears, where we going?\N- This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.30,1:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快\NMove.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.68,1:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.35,1:11:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是俄国人，好像是警察
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.58,1:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不过他们比警察更厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.54,1:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,派点人来，他们杀了很多人，快点啊，我们需要...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.43,1:11:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉张，尽快拿到那个数字然后把跑腿的干掉
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.00,1:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这个数字由我们自己来破解
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.21,1:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.84,1:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天堂之门到了\N- 把我们这样的罪人拒之门外\N- The gates of paradise.\N- Locked and bolted to sinners like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.59,1:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，别浪费时间\NYeah, well,\Nlet's not wait for an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.45,1:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，你个混蛋，快点开始\NAll right, you bastard. Get started.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.55,1:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,下面按我说的做\NHere's how we do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.84,1:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们先放下枪，我再开保险箱\NYou put down your guns, I open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.22,1:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们想杀我，随意\NIf you wanna shoot me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.68,1:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快点决定，真警察马上就要到了\NMake your minds up quick\N'cause the real cops'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.77,1:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,放到地上\NOn the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.27,1:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，你个混蛋，你想干什么？\NCome on, you son of a bitch.\NWhat are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.52,1:13:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,密码左右方向反了，马上就开了\NI had right left switched.\NIt's gonna open.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.96,1:14:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活着的\NYou'll live.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.96,1:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,左26\NLeft 26.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.35,1:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沃夫队长，这里发生了什么？\NCaptain Wolf,\Nwhat the hell happened in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.31,1:14:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为发生了什么，哈？我们突袭了这里\NWhat do you think happened, huh?\NWe had a raid on the place go bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.23,1:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有人员伤亡，赶紧给我进去处理\NWe got dead cops, casualties.\NGet in there, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.57,1:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沃夫队长，你需要救护车\N- 我需要一排救护车\N- Captain Wolf, you need an ambulance.\N- I need a fleet of ambulances.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.36,1:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧叫救护车，懂吗？我自己开去医院\NCall it in, will you? I'll take\Nmy own busted ass to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.37,1:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,演技不错\NNot bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.04,1:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不是个两面派，我几乎都喜欢上你了\NIf you werert such a double-dealing\Nasshole, I could almost like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.00,1:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是几乎！开车！\NAlmost. Drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.63,1:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只是划伤\NIt's a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.55,1:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀你，但我可没说让你住大酒店\NI'm not gonna kill you, but I didn't say\NI was putting you up at the Ritz.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.69,1:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沃夫\NWolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.36,1:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要钱，丹尼\N{\i1}I have your money, Danny.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.11,1:15:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.82,1:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你听见了\NYou heard me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.66,1:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,三千万！五千份一千美元的支票\N30 million. Five-thousand\Nand one-thousand dollar bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.20,1:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想谈谈\N- 不行\N{\i1}- I wanna talk.\N- No.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.12,1:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要的是冷静下来我们好谈点正常的\NNo, what you wanna do is calm down\Nso we can talk like adults.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.71,1:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，丹尼\N{\i1}Shut it, Danny.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.50,1:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想谈，不过不是和你谈\N{\i1}I wanna talk,\Nbut I don't wanna talk to you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.80,1:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你男朋友谈\N{\i1}I wanna talk to your boyfriend.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.68,1:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是亚历克斯\NThis is Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.51,1:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见，亚历克斯\N{\i1}Been a while, Alex.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.14,1:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么拿到这号码的？\N- 别这样，亚历克斯\N- How'd you get this number?\N- Come on, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.73,1:15:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,顺着市长的味就能找到你\NReach up the mayor's ass, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.06,1:15:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,男人就该有男人样，哈？\NA mars gotta do\Nwhat a mars gotta do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.65,1:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他总比安妮这诱饵好\NHe's a better catch\Nthan Annie was anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.90,1:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直不解你为什么会勾搭上那样一头奶牛\N{\i1}I never understood\Nhow you hooked up with a cow like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.41,1:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不是因为她的长相，而是她的幽默感\NIt was never about her looks.\NIt was her sense of humour.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.24,1:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在没那么搞笑了，不是么？\NShe's not so funny now, is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.62,1:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是了，我也一样\NNo, she's not. Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.04,1:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到了钱，亚历克斯，我杀了很多人才弄到的\NI have the money, Alex.\NI had to kill a lot of people to get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.00,1:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以听着\N{\i1}So listen up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.80,1:16:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没交换过密码，另一个保险箱里是什么？\NYou haven't made the combination\Nexchange yet. What's in the other safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.22,1:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一张碟片\NA disc.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.88,1:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,名字，钱的来龙去脉…\NNames, money trails.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.64,1:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,当指挥官派我们帮丹尼清理城市时\N{\i1}When our commanders sent the two of us\Nto help Danny clean up the city,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.81,1:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们附加了一个条件\N{\i1}they attached a price.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.02,1:16:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,作为交换，丹尼要自寻财路\NIn exchange, Danny looked the other way
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.73,1:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而每笔被当做恐怖组织查抄的集团资金\Nwhile the assets seized from every group\Ndeemed a terrorist organisation
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.86,1:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,则装进了他们的私人腰包\Nwere funnelled\Ninto their private accounts.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.90,1:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,惊讶是他们受惊需要保护时\N{\i1}Amazing what people\Nlet you get away with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.65,1:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,却把你赶走了\N{\i1}when they're scared\Nand wanna feel protected.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.74,1:16:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,惊讶的是有那么多小人\NAmazing how many scumbags\Nthere are out there
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.74,1:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,都等着乘机牟利\Nwaiting to take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.49,1:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难道你没有么？\N- 我退出了\N{\i1}- Like you didn't?\N- I quit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.28,1:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为这能帮那些被你私自送去见上帝的人\NBet that helps all those souls you sent\Nto meet their maker without due process
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.45,1:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,省下很多功夫吗？\Nrest a whole lot easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.79,1:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你在拳击场上\N{\i1}You thought you could atone\Nby climbing into a cage{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.91,1:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,被人随意殴打就能赎罪吗？\N{\i1}and allowing yourself\Nto get beaten to a pulp?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.17,1:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别给我说教了，路克！\N{\i1}Don't fucking preach at me, Luke.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.09,1:17:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是收钱办事\NI'm getting paid for services rendered.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.01,1:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，你把碟片卖给中国人好让他们勒索我们上司\N{\i1}Right. You sell the disc to the Chinese\Nso they can blackmail our old honchos,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.63,1:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然后拿着三千万美元和丹尼去巴哈马别墅逍遥自在\N{\i1}take the 30 mill and waltz off\Nwith Danny to a villa in the Bahamas.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.51,1:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是巴厘岛，不过无所谓了，不是么？\NBali, but whatever, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.22,1:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，就算你知道了，又如何？\NSo, now you know. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.48,1:17:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你要应付我\N{\i1}Now you're dealing with me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.48,1:17:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧，我退出\N- 不行\N{\i1}- All right, I'm turning around.\N- No, you're not.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.23,1:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？你已经拿到钱了\NWhat are you talking about?\NYou've got the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.03,1:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 中国人手里没有我要的了\N- 不，他们有我想要的\N{\i1}- The Chinese have nothing I care about.\N- No. They have something I do.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.84,1:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把你保险箱密码给这女孩，她会给你我们的\NGive the girl the combination to your\Nsafe and she will give you our number.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.68,1:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到你的地方，你去我们的\NWe go to your location, you go to ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.64,1:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们拿到碟片，我们会给你解密密码\NWhen we've gotten the disc,\Nwe will explain the code
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.14,1:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到你的钱\Nand you'll get the cash.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.15,1:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一言为定\NThat's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.90,1:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说说看吧\N- 这是个很长的数字\N- Let's hear it.\N- It's a very long number.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.19,1:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好能记下来\NYou'll want to write it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.86,1:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝我还带了笔，哈？\NThank goodness I brought a pen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.75,1:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好闭上眼睛\NYou might wanna close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.67,1:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,随你便吧\NHave it your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.56,1:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快接，路克\NCome on, Luke.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.77,1:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,老地方，就你和我\N{\i1}The old place, just you and me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.03,1:18:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是路克的朋友吗？\NYou're a friend of Luke?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.07,1:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你该关心的\NNot as far as you're concerned.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.30,1:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚席卷整个纽约的暴力活动\N{\i1}The violence\Nthat has rocked the city tonight{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.63,1:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,依旧持续，不到一小时前\N{\i1}continued in a bloody gun battle{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.17,1:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,中国城一家夜总会爆发了血腥枪战\N{\i1}in a Chinatown nightclub\Nless than an hourago.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.30,1:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这已经完全失控了\N- 你以为呢？\N- This is really getting out of hand.\N- You think?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.72,1:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢提醒\NThanks for that insight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.93,1:19:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,市长，亚历克斯·罗瑟斯在你私人专线上\NYour Honour,\NAlex Rosers on your private line.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.93,1:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他说有急事\NHe says that it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.60,1:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打扰一下，市长\N- 我5分钟后回来，现在别烦我\N- Excuse me, Your Honour.\N- Back in five. Don't bother me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.11,1:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么不打我手机？\NWhy didn't he call me on my cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.48,1:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得让你把所有电话都接到我的…\NI thought I told you to put\Nall my calls through to the...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.36,1:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直跟你说这里保安水平太差\NI always told you this place\Nhad lousy security standards.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.74,1:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为没人会疯到像你一样来这杀人\NBecause nobody's been crazy enough to\Ncome in here and pull a stunt like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.08,1:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有种，路克\N- 是啊，真是惊讶我还能走路\N- You got some balls, Luke.\N- Yeah, amazing I can even walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.04,1:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给我碟片\NThe disc.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.75,1:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？你以为我会傻到让中国帮派\NWhat, you think I'm stupid enough\Nto let a gang of Chinese
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.25,1:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,穿过前门进到房间来拿它？\Nwalk up the front steps and collect it\Nfrom me in my living room?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.84,1:19:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它在离这很远的保险箱里\N- 我不认为你很蠢\N- It's in a safe far away from here.\N- I don't think you're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.68,1:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不认为你只有一份拷贝\NWhich is why I don't for a second\Nbelieve you gave away the only copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.93,1:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去见亚历克斯\NI'm going to meet Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.31,1:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你先给我碟片，不然我就在非要害的部位给你一枪\NFirst you give me the disc or I'll put\Nbullets in places that won't kill you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.94,1:20:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让你下半辈子生不如死\Nbut make you spend\Nthe rest of your life wishing I had.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.41,1:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,满意了?\NSatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.16,1:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确认一下这不是“金刚葫芦娃”\N{\i1}I wanna make sure\Nit's not ABBA'sGreatest Hits.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.50,1:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯会杀了你的,你知道的\NAlex will kill you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.55,1:20:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，或许吧\NYeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.76,1:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝，路克，你气色很不好\NJesus. Luke, you look like hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.98,1:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,酒精而已，缺少睡眠和阳光\NJust alcohol, lack of sunlight,\Nsleep deprivation.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.23,1:21:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,除此以外，我感觉不错\NOther than that, I feel great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.32,1:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呵，我在想，我们在这里抛过多少尸了？\NYou know, I was thinking, how many\Nbodies have we dumped in this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.83,1:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的，我从不记数\NYou know, I didn't keep count.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.50,1:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是混蛋，不是么？\NThey were all assholes, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.54,1:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,放开她，亚历克斯\NLet her go, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.17,1:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼打电话说你去拜访过他\NDanny called.\NHe told me about your visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.84,1:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不承认，我都没想到这一手\NI have to admit,\Neven I didn't see that one coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.81,1:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在有了钱和碟片\NYou had the disc and the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.02,1:22:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么...\NWhat...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.60,1:22:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她对你来说意味着什么？\NWhat is she to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.98,1:22:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,生命\NLife.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.90,1:22:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，趁还有命就好好享受吧\NWell, enjoy it while it lasts,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.49,1:22:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不久她就会让你的小命玩完的\N'cause she's the reason\Nyours is gonna be a whole lot shorter.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.24,1:22:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,钱在哪，路克\NThe money, Luke.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.45,1:22:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在车里\NIn the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.38,1:22:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,或者银行里\NOr in the bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.92,1:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或者在中央车站储物柜里\NOr in a series of lockers\Nat Grand Central.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.68,1:22:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我可能出于好心悉数捐出了\NOr maybe I donated it to charity,\Nout of the goodness of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.89,1:22:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想要知道下落，你就得来硬的\NYou wanna find out where that money is,\Nyou're gonna have to do it the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.91,1:23:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧，梅？\NYou all right, Mei?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.49,1:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过他打斗，你打不过他的\NI saw him fight before.\NBad business for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.71,1:23:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，最糟的是\NYeah. The worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.13,1:23:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你又救了我\NYou saved me, again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.34,1:24:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们救了对方\NWe save each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.76,1:24:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么\NI know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.64,1:24:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我把这垃圾弄出来\NHelp me get this sack of garbage\Nout of the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.27,1:24:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,确保他安全回到他老爸那儿\NMake sure he gets to his daddy\Nsafe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.03,1:24:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,5万，赔偿你的损失\N50 grand, for your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.45,1:24:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,钱可能不多，但至少你有命花\NMight not seem like much, but at least\Nyou're gonna live to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.49,1:24:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在经历了这么多后，你还想放过他？\NYou want him safe and sound\Nafter what he did to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.62,1:24:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为了她\NFor her sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.25,1:24:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,若再见面，你就万事皆休\NWe meet again, all bets are off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.69,1:24:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最尊敬的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.30,1:24:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有两千九百九十五万美元
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.04,1:24:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会还余下的5万，再加10%的利息
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.14,1:24:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果万一您还生气
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.29,1:24:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须告诉您，我知道您在中国城生意的每一个帐号
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.63,1:25:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有汇钱到中国的途径
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.51,1:25:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您不找我们的麻烦，我们也不会找您的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.29,1:25:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,来追我们的话，你的世界就完了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.28,1:25:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证说话算话
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.17,1:25:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,给我准备飞机票
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.42,1:25:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到这个
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.79,1:25:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼地方！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.43,1:25:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你妈的给我看路，哥们！\N- 走你的\N- Watch where you're fucking going, man!\N- Keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.89,1:25:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？再说一遍？啥？\N- 走开\N- Excuse me? Pardon me? Anything?\N- Walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.31,1:25:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他妈的纽约！\NThis is fucking New York City!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.86,1:25:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 第五家银行了，还有几家？\N- 没了\N- Bank number five. How many more?\N- That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.91,1:25:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在碟片拷贝已遍布城市保险柜\NGot copies of the disc\Nin security boxes all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.00,1:25:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们出事\NAnything happens to us,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.41,1:25:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很多大人物就得倒霉\Na lot of important people\Nare gonna be very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.75,1:25:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的护身符，这是笔好生意\NOur security. Good business for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.00,1:26:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在干嘛？\N- 我们离开这里\N- What now?\N- Now we get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.13,1:26:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,梅，你是个孩子…我不确定自己能否做个好父亲\NMei, you're a kid and...\NI'm not sure I could be a good father.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.60,1:26:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我能力不足\NI think that ship has sailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.52,1:26:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要父亲\NI don't want no more fathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.90,1:26:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以做我朋友吗？\NWill you be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.48,1:26:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,至死都愿\NTill my dying day.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.03,1:26:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到一家在西雅图专门培训天才儿童的学校\NI got info on a school\Nfor gifted kids up in Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.08,1:26:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这会是次美妙旅行，如果你喜欢那里的风光的话\NIt's a nice drive,\Nif you like trees and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.96,1:26:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们安全了吗？\NAre we safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.25,1:26:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别想太多，梅，别想太多\NOne day at a time, Mei.\NOne day at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.05,1:26:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,=-全片完，谢谢观赏-=\N更多精彩影视，尽在HDCHINA.ORG

